attributionInfo.brokerName: Coldwell Banker Sea Coast Advantage - Jacksonville
Coldwell Banker Sea Coast Advantage - Jacksonville

data.description: Welcome home to cozy perfection! This 3-bed, 2-bath gem nestled on a charming corner lot in Jacksonville, NC, invites you to embrace warmth and comfort. Picture yourself beneath the inviting vaulted ceilings in the living room with fireplace, creating an intimate space to unwind, complete with flat screen tv. The heart of this home is the snug eat-in kitchen, where memories are made around the table. A spacious bonus room offers the perfect spot for your personal retreat. As a bonus, the washer and dryer come with! Ready to cozy up in your dream home? Contact a dedicated REALTOR(r) today for your personal tour of this charming haven!
